AIX Port for liblogging

Issue-32: stdlog should support functionality like the syslog LOG_PID option

Implement a STDLOG_PID option to specify that each log message should be tagged
with the process identifier as well as the ident. This is done in the format
"ident[pid]" as described in RFC-3164. This is honored by both the file: and
uxsock: channel drivers.

Update the test program to allow use of the STDLOG_PID option.
maintain ChangeLog

So we replace it with the actual file name. That is a bit unelegant,
but works... ;-)

Issue 28: sigsafe_printf does not recognize the "j" length modifier

Modify the __stdlog_sigsafe_printf() function so that it recognizes
the "j" length modifier indicating that the argument is of type
intmax_t (e.g., "%jd") or uintmax_t (e.g., "%ju").
